reviewText: Wish it was longer. A little too expensive for the amount of entertainment but then again it a Canadian product and it is just normally more expensive.
Very funny and entertaining show for the family. My family enjoyed watching every minute of it and it bought a good lough on all of us.

This volume 7&8 contains mostly exactly the same footage of earlier Just For Laughs videos. What a rip-off! What a waste of money. There are a few new gags, but the repeat footage doesn't even have new actors or victims, just what was in earlier vols.
